WINDOWS
Ctrl+5 = paragraph spacing 1.5
Shift+F3 = change Uppercase


MAC
Cmd+shit + > = increase font
cmd+< = decrease font
ctrl+tab = tab in a table
option+cmd+c = uppercase
cmd+e = center
cmd+l = left
cmd+r = right
cmd+j = justify
cmd+shift+c = copy formatting
cmd+shift+v = paste formatting
cmd+8 = show formatting marks
cmd + < = change color to the text

